  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6479503/" class="title-link">大家通俗读本</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6479503"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/xpwk/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u46591140-8.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/xpwk/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">罗成</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-12-26"
      class="main-meta">2013-12-26 18:38:02</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6479503_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这是资中筠先生的在国家图书馆美国系列讲座的文字整理，通俗易懂，纠正很多，中国人关于美国认识的错误常识，也比较系统，但是比之前的书来说要随意一些，大量插图，内容着实不多，作为休闲读物不错，是在是太通俗了。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6479503/#comments">(1回应)</a>
